{"tid":297909,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"800萬以上物業最多承按80%","createTime":"2017-06-26T00:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T00:45:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37a9bc5d1cd101199a024a881f7ed4bc480937d3","tid":297909,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】安老按揭申請個案近年增加，申請者每月平均獲年金1.49萬元，不過值得注意的是估值800萬元以上物業，只能按樓價60%至80%計算年金，而即使物業價值逾億元，年金計算上限僅為1,500萬元。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170626/large/b0302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170626%2Flarge%2Fb0302a.gif&h=3df1736c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170626/large/17848618z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170626%2Flarge%2F17848618z.jpg&h=4fac26b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李兆波指，趁樓價升至歷史新高申請安老按揭是明智決定，但申請前必須清楚計劃細節。　資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n隨着樓價升溫，不少長者趁高價承造安老按揭，鎖定物業價值。不過計算年金的物業估值亦有上限，除800萬元或以下物業可全額計算年金外，800萬元以上只能按60%至80%樓價計算年金，計算上限為1,500萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>李兆波：趁高價申請屬明智</strong><br />\n<br />\n以太古城青松閣一單位為例，根據上周五匯豐物業估價，單位估值1,495萬元，若承造安老按揭需打八折，即樓價只計算1,046.5萬元。以60歲長者計，若選擇20年年金，每月可取得2.5萬元至80歲；若選擇終身領取，每月亦有2.1萬元。<br />\n中文大學商學院助理院長李兆波指，趁樓價升至歷史新高申請安老按揭是明智決定，但申請前必須清楚計劃細節，並與子女溝通好。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府亦即將推出終身年金。李兆波認為，長者申請安老按揭後，若覺得現金流仍然不夠，可將積蓄投資公共年金雙管齊下。不過，由於公共年金內部回報率只有4%，若然長者有投資經驗則可自行投資，不一定將資金鎖死在年金計劃。<br />\n<br />\n【各類物業例子】<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170626/large/b0302b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170626%2Flarge%2Fb0302b.gif&h=b37e748f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170626/large/b0302c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170626%2Flarge%2Fb0302c.gif&h=7fd47411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170626/large/b0302c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170626%2Flarge%2Fb0302c.gif&h=7fd47411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170626/20068791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170626%2F20068791&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=cb690d34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170626%2F20068791&h=1c6926ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170626/20068791</a>"},{"pid":"a7f38412473003414b58cad4862b16687d677ede","tid":297909,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:11:26.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724070726cfb69e594c48f00b8cf8afe545aad37","tid":297909,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63446130894fbcf07a8a8b99086ac68aa57bf75a","tid":297909,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"逆按揭，標題令人以為正式按揭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}